<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <title>Document</title>
  </head>
  <body style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">
    <section class="page-break" style="position: relative; margin: 5%">
      <div class="permitToDig">
        <div>
          <img class="logo" src="http://localhost:5000/images/templateImages/logo.png" alt="logo" />
          <div>
            <h1>PERMIT TO DIG CHECKLIST</h1>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p>Project:</p>
          <p>Job No.:</p>
        </div>
        <div
          style="
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            border-bottom: 2px solid black;
            border-top: 2px solid black;
            padding: 5px;
          "
        >
          <span>No.:</span>
          <span>Date Issued:</span>
          <span>Date of Expiry:</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p><b></b> OPERATION:</b></p>
          <p>
            This permit is issued to:(name) ________________ Signed  Of (Which company) ________________ location: ________________ 
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p>
            Sketch indicating location and number of services (drawing attached
            where appropriate).
          </p>
          <div style="width: 100%; height: 200px;">
            <img
              class="sketch"
              src="http://localhost:5000/images/documents/{{permit_to_dig_sketch_image}}"
              alt="Sketch"
            />
          </div>
          <p><b>Permit isuued by:</b></p>
          <p>(Sign and print name below signature)</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p>
            <b
              >Tick/Delete and sign each of the following to show that relevant
              action has been taken:</b
            >
          </p>
          <table>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <th></th>
                <th>Action</th>
                <th>Date</th>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>a) Method Statement explained to operatives:</td>
                <td></td>
                <td></td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>b) Stats. Drawings available and used:</td>
                <td></td>
                <td></td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>c) Assitance from Stats. Authority required:</td>
                <td></td>
                <td></td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  d) Visual inspection carried out: (Street lighting, valve
                  cover etc.)
                </td>
                <td></td>
                <td></td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>e) C.A.T Used: (Competent Person).</td>
                <td></td>
                <td></td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>f) Services marked on site: (Spraypaint etc.)</td>
                <td></td>
                <td></td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>g) Trial holes/trenches dug:</td>
                <td></td>
                <td></td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>h) Method of sale digging: - Hand Tools:</td>
                <td></td>
                <td></td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  i) Are there services of an unsual nature? (e.g. Oil,
                  Chemical).
                </td>
                <td></td>
                <td></td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
          <p>
            <b>A COPY OF THIS PERMIT IS TO BE PRESENT AT EACH EXCAVATION DIG</b>
          </p>
          <p>
            TRACE, LOCATE AND MARK ALL SERVICES | Remember Other Services May Be
            Present
          </p>
          <div
            style="
              display: flex;
              justify-content: space-around;
              border-bottom: 2px solid black;
              padding: 5px;
            "
          >
            <span>Permit Closed By:</span>
            <span>Time:</span>
            <span>Date:</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <style>
      .permitToDig p {
        font-size: 11px;
      }

      .permitToDig .logo {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        right: 0;
        width: 100px;
        height: 50px;
      }

      .permitToDig table {
        border-collapse: collapse;
        width: 100%;
        margin-top: 5px;
      }

      .permitToDig th,
      .permitToDig td {
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
        padding: 6px;
        text-align: left;
      }

      .permitToDig th {
        background-color: #f2f2f2;
      }

      .permitToDig tr {
        height: 36px;
      }

      .permitToDig .sketch {
        height: 200px;
        width: auto;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      .permitToDig caption {
        font-weight: bold;
        background-color: #333;
        color: #fff;
        padding: 6px;
      }

      .permitToDig .page-break {
        page-break-after: always;
      }
    </style>
  </body>
</html>
